% The rho translation of the same instance: the gate<->token rendezvous and the
% released continuation are extra INTERNAL (tau) steps. Branching-bisimilar to the
% CA side (sequential taus are inert), the mCRL2 image of the translation being a
% faithful relabelling up to internal computation.
act tok, fire, settle;
proc TR = tok . tau . fire . tau . settle . delta;
init TR;
